In direct purchase of bad loans, the government will aggressively intervene to ensure that management money is not exaggerated.
This includes the fact that existing golden parachute contracts do not change, the restriction only applies to new ones to encourage participation in the programme.
This is the first time in American history that there will be a legal restriction on the remuneration of CEOs - commented the chairman of the House's Financial Services Committee, Barney Frank of the Democratic Party.
In addition, in the banks participating in the programme, the State acquires the right to acquire a holding, thus reducing the risk of taxpayers, as they can ultimately win the transaction as soon as the economy and the bank saved with it recovers.
